extends layout

block content
    section.page-top-section.set-bg(data-setbg='/img/page-top-bg.jpg')
        .container.text-white
            h2 Frequently Asked Questions

    .site-breadcrumb
        .container
            a(href='/')
                i.fa.fa-home
                | Home
            span
                i.fa.fa-angle-right
                | FAQ

    section.page-section.faq-page
        .container
            .row
                .col-lg-12
                    .accordion#faqAccordion
                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingOne
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseOne' aria-expanded='true' aria-controls='collapseOne')
                                        | 1. What does QANDOS do?
                            #collapseOne.collapse.show(aria-labelledby='headingOne' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | QANDOS provides secure property verification, transaction advisory, and escrow-facilitated real estate acquisition services to eliminate fraud and risk.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingTwo
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseTwo' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseTwo')
                                        | 2. Do you sell property directly?
                            #collapseTwo.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingTwo' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | No. We verify and secure property transactions. We may introduce verified opportunities but act primarily as a trust and transaction security partner.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingThree
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseThree' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseThree')
                                        | 3. How does your verification work?
                            #collapseThree.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingThree' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    p Our process includes:
                                    ul
                                        li Title and registry checks
                                        li Survey verification
                                        li Legal review
                                        li Physical inspection
                                        li Risk advisory report

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingFour
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseFour' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseFour')
                                        | 4. Do you work with Nigerians in the diaspora?
                            #collapseFour.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingFour' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | Yes. A large portion of our clients are diaspora investors seeking safe property acquisition in Nigeria.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingFive
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseFive' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseFive')
                                        | 5. What is escrow and how does it protect me?
                            #collapseFive.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingFive' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | Escrow ensures funds are held securely and only released when agreed transaction conditions are met, protecting both buyer and seller.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingSix
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseSix' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseSix')
                                        | 6. How long does verification take?
                            #collapseSix.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingSix' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | Typically 3â€“10 working days depending on location and documentation availability.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingSeven
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseSeven' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseSeven')
                                        | 7. What are your fees?
                            #collapseSeven.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingSeven' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    p Fees depend on:
                                    ul
                                        li Property value
                                        li Verification scope
                                        li Transaction complexity
                                    p A clear quote is provided before engagement.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingEight
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseEight' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseEight')
                                        | 8. Do you guarantee property safety?
                            #collapseEight.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingEight' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | We provide professional verification and risk assessment. Where applicable, insured or guaranteed transactions will be clearly stated.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingNine
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseNine' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseNine')
                                        | 9. Where do you operate?
                            #collapseNine.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingNine' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | Currently focused on Abuja with expansion across major African cities planned.

                        .card.mb-3
                            .card-header#headingTen
                                h5.mb-0
                                    button.btn.btn-link.collapsed(type='button' data-toggle='collapse' data-target='#collapseTen' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseTen')
                                        | 10. How do I get started?
                            #collapseTen.collapse(aria-labelledby='headingTen' data-parent='#faqAccordion')
                                .card-body
                                    | Email: info@qandos.com Or request a secure consultation via our website.
